data.description:
Beautiful sun filled townhome with cross breezes from your two decks.
Home is well maintained, new siding, all newer windows and three patio doors,
newer kitchen maple cabinets, new dish washer, new refrigerator, center island,
pantry, Large window above the kitchen sink. off kitchen is ½ bath a spacious living
room/fireplace. Upper level has 3 bedroom with one an office/loft/bedroom. Primary
bedroom has large picture window its own bath and a walk- in closet. Laundry is on
the garage level. Walkout basement family room with cathedral ceiling and access to
the patio. {Full list of updates located in supplements}
